TreeNode *searchBST(TreeNode *root, const int &val) {         if (!root)             return nullptr;         if (root->val == val)             return root;         return val > root->val ? searchBST(root->right, val) : searchBST(root->left, val);     }

TreeNode *insertIntoBST(TreeNode *root, int val) {         TreeNode *child = root;         while (child) {             if (val > child->val) {                 if (!child->right) {                     auto *temp = new TreeNode(val);                     child->right = temp;                     break;                 }                 child = child->right;             } else {                 if (!child->left) {                     auto *temp = new TreeNode(val);                     child->left = temp;                     break;                 }                 child = child->left;             }         }         return root;     }
